PREP:\
Know their value proposition\
Have an understanding of influencing market factors\
Pitches are short stories, and this is about you so make it interesting; if you sound uninspired they will think you are\
Keep it short; don't use unnecessary words or explain\
Address Budget, Authority, NEed and Time Objections preemptively\
